main event: Various observers watched a round shaped silver-colored object pass over the horizon in the western sky.
interesting points: The object appeared to be traveling at a high rate of speed., Military personnel on the scene reported watching the object until it disappeared., It was described as being 20 yards in diameter., Observers noted inside lights observed on the object., The sighting lasted for about 20 minutes before the object disappeared.
witness description: Civilian, 36 years old, carpenter; military personnel; husband-wife, farmer.
